import React from 'react';
import {
  Container,
  Typography,
  Grid,
  Card,
  CardContent,
  CardMedia,
  Box,
  Divider,
} from '@mui/material';
import { styled } from '@mui/material/styles';

const StyledCard = styled(Card)(({ theme }) => ({
  height: '100%',
  display: 'flex',
  flexDirection: 'column',
  transition: 'transform 0.3s ease-in-out',
  '&:hover': {
    transform: 'translateY(-5px)',
  },
}));

const teamMembers = [
  {
    name: 'John Smith',
    role: 'Founder & Lead Guide',
    bio: 'With over 15 years of experience in tourism, John brings extensive knowledge of Malta\'s history and culture.',
    image: 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1507003211169-0a1dd7228f2d?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=MnwxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8&auto=format&fit=crop&w=774&q=80',
  },
  {
    name: 'Maria Garcia',
    role: 'Tour Coordinator',
    bio: 'Maria ensures every tour runs smoothly and guests have the best possible experience.',
    image: 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1494790108377-be9c29b29330?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=MnwxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8&auto=format&fit=crop&w=774&q=80',
  },
  {
    name: 'David Brown',
    role: 'History Expert',
    bio: 'David holds a PhD in Mediterranean History and brings academic expertise to our tours.',
    image: 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1500648767791-00dcc994a43e?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=MnwxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8&auto=format&fit=crop&w=774&q=80',
  },
];

function About() {
  return (
    <Container sx={{ py: 8 }}>
      <Typography variant="h4" component="h1" gutterBottom>
        About Malta Tour Guide
      </Typography>
      
      <Box sx={{ my: 4 }}>
        <Typography variant="body1" paragraph>
          Welcome to Malta Tour Guide, your premier destination for exploring the rich history and stunning landscapes of Malta. Founded in 2010, we have been providing exceptional guided tours to thousands of visitors from around the world.
        </Typography>
        <Typography variant="body1" paragraph>
          Our mission is to create unforgettable experiences by sharing our passion for Malta's unique heritage, from its ancient temples to its medieval cities and crystal-clear waters. We believe in sustainable tourism and work closely with local communities to preserve Malta's cultural treasures.
        </Typography>
      </Box>

      <Divider sx={{ my: 4 }} />

      <Typography variant="h5" component="h2" gutterBottom>
        Our Team
      </Typography>
      <Grid container spacing={4} sx={{ mt: 2 }}>
        {teamMembers.map((member) => (
          <Grid item key={member.name} xs={12} sm={6} md={4}>
            <StyledCard>
              <CardMedia
                component="img"
                height="300"
                image={member.image}
                alt={member.name}
              />
              <CardContent>
                <Typography gutterBottom variant="h6" component="h3">
                  {member.name}
                </Typography>
                <Typography variant="subtitle1" color="text.secondary" gutterBottom>
                  {member.role}
                </Typography>
                <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                  {member.bio}
                </Typography>
              </CardContent>
            </StyledCard>
          </Grid>
        ))}
      </Grid>

      <Box sx={{ my: 6 }}>
        <Typography variant="h5" component="h2" gutterBottom>
          Why Choose Us?
        </Typography>
        <Grid container spacing={4}>
          <Grid item xs={12} md={4}>
            <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>
              Expert Guides
            </Typography>
            <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
              Our guides are passionate locals with extensive knowledge of Malta's history and culture.
            </Typography>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12} md={4}>
            <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>
              Small Groups
            </Typography>
            <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
              We keep our groups small to ensure a personalized experience for every guest.
            </Typography>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12} md={4}>
            <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>
              Sustainable Tourism
            </Typography>
            <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
              We are committed to preserving Malta's heritage and supporting local communities.
            </Typography>
          </Grid>
        </Grid>
      </Box>
    </Container>
  );
}

export default About;
